<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/sep/06/">&#x27a0;</a> September 6, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="apple-all-iphone-customers" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.apple.com/hotnews/openiphoneletter/">Apple - To all iPhone customers</a></h4>

        
            
        

